metadata.name: The fortune-teller Pepe
metadata.description:
The fortune-teller Pepe stares at the sky and monitors the movement of stars and planets.She believes that the future is Pepe's.Pepes will cover the whole world.


It’s my illustration artwork which took 6 days to make it. It’s full of details and made with digital tools.

3000 * 3000 Pixels
